page.title: 05FORESTRY
page.content: The forest in our area is called Melbury.There are lots of different trees in the forest: Norway Spruce, Sitka Spruce, Corsican Pine, Lodge_pole Pine and some Red Oak. The trees in our area are about fifty_seven years old. The wood is used for the wood pulp industry.They used a grabber to pick up the logs. The grabber is on the front of a lorry that carries the logs the grabber puts the logs on the back of the lorry. There are other forestry jobs to do: Making Public foot_paths through the Forest and making public roads through the Forest. There is a lot of wildlife in the forest: Deer, Foxes, Badgers, Squirrels, Rabbits and vat numbers of insects.
